    "text": "$$\n\\int_{0}^{5} [4f(x) - 3x^2]dx = 4\\int_{0}^{5} f(x)dx - \\int_{0}^{5} 3x^2dx = -8 - x^3 \\Big|_{0}^{5} = -8 - 125 = -133.\n$$"
